WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.183
[AUDIO YO‘Q]

00:00:03.183 --> 00:00:06.623
Xuddi urg‘ularga o‘xshab, Sharqiy 
sohilda G‘arbiy sohilga qaraganda 

00:00:06.623 --> 00:00:10.800
so‘zlarni aytilishi boshqacha
 urg‘uda bo‘lishi mumkin.

00:00:10.800 --> 00:00:18.010
Hattoki har xil oilalarda ham, 
bu farqni kuzatish mumkin.

00:00:18.010 --> 00:00:21.890
lekin umumiy qaraganda, ya’ni 
Janubiy, Markaziy, Shimoliy va 

00:00:21.890 --> 00:00:27.750
barchalari juda o‘xshash talaffuzga ega,
 men ’looty’ so‘zini aytganimday.

00:00:27.750 --> 00:00:33.810
Bu tovush tilingizni tishingiz 
orqasiga qo‘yib T deganingizda hosil bo‘ladi.

00:00:33.810 --> 00:00:37.150
Ammo T ni talaffuz qilishni
 uchta har xil yo‘li bor,

00:00:37.150 --> 00:00:40.070
Masalan, qattiq T, yumshoq T, yoki 

00:00:40.070 --> 00:00:45.089
cho‘zilgan T bor va sizning talaffuzingizga
 qarab u o‘zgarishi mumkin. 

00:00:45.089 --> 00:00:52.890
O‘ylashimcha, sohilda, tekisliklarda,
ko‘l va Miwok ning har qanday mintaqasida 

00:00:52.890 --> 00:00:57.669
yashaydiganlar uchun alohida ilova 
yaratish kerak, agar talab bo‘lsa, albatta. 

